  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13052372/inghams_lakes-and-mountains-preview-2018.png" alt="Lakes &amp; Mountains Preview 2018" rel="486,453" /></div>
<div style="height: 15px; font-size: x-small; text-align: center;">New Inghams Lakes &amp; Mountains Preview 2018 brochure.</div>
<div></div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>Inghams has launched its Lakes &amp; Mountains Summer 2018 preview brochure with FROZEN PRICES and a range of EARLY BOOKING OFFERS, saving up to £660 per couple if booked before 30<sup>th</sup> September 2017.</p>
<p>The new brochure features over 100 European resorts, cities and tours, including the NEW Slovenia and Austria twin-centre option. Holiday durations are fully flexible, with seven, 10 and 14-night stays, as well as a choice of twin-centre resort combinations, escorted rail tours, short breaks and city breaks.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Frozen Prices<br /></span>For early bookings, all prices in the Lakes &amp; Mountains Summer 2018 preview brochure have been held at Summer 2017 levels. To helps guests’ budgets stretch further, Inghams has also frozen the prices of many of its pre-bookable excursions and Swiss walking &amp; travel passes to Summer 2017 levels, until 30<sup>th</sup> September 2017.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">What’s New?<br /></span>Inghams has expanded its partner hotel range to include two new properties for Summer 2018. The three-star, family-friendly Hotel Pavillon des Fleurs on the shores of Lake Annecy, France, is perfect for those looking to be active in a beautiful location. Prices start from £819 per person for seven nights. In Austria, the three-diamond Chalet Linda in Kitzbühel offers guests a relaxed base (just five minutes’ walk from the village centre) from which to explore this fashionable resort and its surroundings. Prices start from £559 per person for seven nights.</p>
<p>Inghams Lakes &amp; Mountains’ most highly-anticipated new product for Summer 2018 is a two-country holiday to Slovenia and Austria:</p>
<p>Guests can visit Slovenia’s charming mountain resort of Kranjska Gora, stunning Lake Bled or tranquil Lake Bohinj followed by one of Austria’s popular resorts (choose from Kitzbühel, Zell am See or St. Wolfgang) on a 10-night combined holiday from £1,049 per person. The price includes return flights to Salzburg and airport transfers.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Added Value</span> <br />The new brochure also features an extensive range of complimentary extras included in the price of many holidays. These include:</p>
<ul>
<li>FREE guided walks in selected resorts</li>
<li>FREE packed lunches and afternoon tea and cake in all chalets, Chalet Hotels and many partner hotels</li>
<li>HALF PRICE travel throughout Switzerland</li>
<li>FREE use of cable-cars, chairlifts and public transport in many resorts in Austria, Italy, France and Switzerland</li>
<li>FREE bike hire in many hotels</li>
<li>FREE walking maps to over 40 destinations (book before 30<sup>th</sup> September 2017)</li>
<li>NO single supplement at selected hotels</li>
</ul>
<p>To receive a copy of the new brochure, please visit our brochure request page.</p>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="g12">
<p><strong>ENDS. </strong></p>
<p>For bookings, please visit <strong>www.inghams.co.uk, </strong>call <strong>01483 791 116.</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
